title: President Donald J. Trump Signs S. 117 into Law – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			
Issued on:
January 31, 2018
On Wednesday, January 31, 2018, the President signed into law:S. 117, the “Alex Diekmann Peak Designation Act of 2017,” which designates a mountain peak in the State of Montana as the “Alex Diekmann Peak”.
